    public abstract class GAFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
    GAFragment is an abstract class used for sending Lifecycle event to Google Analysis. All fragments extends the GAFragment will automatically sending their Lifecycle event as long as they implement getNameAsGaLabel()
